info.description:
# Peewee Bottle Server

This package provides a set of tools and snippets for development of web-server driven using bottle framework and Peewee ORM.

The package was developed based on the guidelines provided at [python-packaging](https://python-packaging.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html).
